                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p><hr /><p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The mercenary band engages in a coordinated attack with its wide array of melee weapons against each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] with a @Check[reflex|dc:25|basic|options:area-effect] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+2)[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage], @Damage[(1d8+2)[piercing]|options:area-damage]{piercing}, or @Damage[(1d8+2)[slashing]|options:area-damage]{slashing}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(3d8+4)[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage], @Damage[(3d8+4)[piercing]|options:area-damage]{piercing}, or @Damage[(3d8+4)[slashing]|options:area-damage]{slashing}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(4d8+6)[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage], @Damage[(4d8+6)[piercing]|options:area-damage]{piercing}, or @Damage[(4d8+6)[slashing]|options:area-damage]{slashing}</p>"
